data.description: LOWERED PRICE and SELLER MOTIVATED! Welcome to the highly desired Villages of Avalon, a NO-CDD community!  This "LIKE NEW" 2018 home is ready for a new owner and is conveniently located and very close to the Veterans Expwy (less than 5 minutes!).  Built in 2018, only one owner, and ready for you.  With beautiful high ceilings, light colors, bright and light tile flooring will welcome you for a tour.  As you enter through the wide entry hall, to your left you will find two independent rooms big enough to fit a full-size bed and a queen size bed plus more space for your furniture.  In between, the very well-kept bathroom with a tub.  On the other side, a separate laundry room with plenty of space for add-ons.  As you walk inside the house, the extended living/dining room with a huge kitchen will be perfect for gatherings, or to enjoy a nice family meal.  Very modern dark cabinets, with a beautiful island and the granite countertops will motivate your creativity to add any special touches you would like.  All kitchen lighting upgrades are already pre-wired, and you will find plenty of counter space for the busiest kitchens.  Across from the living room, the huge master bedroom is so light and bright, with an upgraded selection of double windows, plus a huge master bathroom with an amazing walk-in closed and a linen closet perfectly located inside. You will find a nice sized shower and enough space for a double sink in the future.  Facing the backyard view, you enjoy not having any houses on the back, and a very convenient access across the back street towards the community pool and your own private Gym included in your HOA.  Backyard holds plenty of outdoor space for you to imagine and create, and concrete slab is already in place.  Built-in pest control system in place. All kitchen appliances, A/C, electrical water heater, and even roof are only some years old (2018), so this property is move-in ready and worry free!
